trans-unit.source: Specifies that a property, field, or parameter should be populated with all matching exports by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Angir at en egenskap, felt eller parameteren må fylles ut med alle samsvarende Eksporter av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.ImportManyAttribute"></xref> class, importing the set of exports with the default contract name.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.ImportManyAttribute"> </xref> klassen import settet med Eksporter med navnet på standardserveren kontrakten.

trans-unit.source: The default contract name is the result of calling the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.AttributedModelServices.GetContractName%2A> method on the type of the property, field, or parameter that is marked with this attribute.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på standardserveren kontrakten er resultatet av kaller den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.AttributedModelServices.GetContractName%2A>-metoden på hva slags egenskap, felt eller parameter som er merket med attributtet.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.AttributedModelServices.GetContractName%2A>

trans-unit.source: The contract name is compared by using the <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A> property to perform a case-sensitive, non-linguistic comparison.

trans-unit.target: Hva slags eksporten å importere.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the decorated property or field will be recomposed when exports that provide the matching contract change.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om dekorerte egenskapen eller feltet vil bli opprettet på nytt ved Eksporter som gir den tilsvarende servicekontrakten endringen.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the property or field allows for recomposition when exports that provide the same <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.ImportManyAttribute.ContractName*> are added or removed from the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer"></xref>; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis egenskapen eller feltet tillater recomposition når Eksporter som inneholder den samme <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.ImportManyAttribute.ContractName*>legges til eller fjernet fra den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer"> </xref>; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.ImportManyAttribute.ContractName*>

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the contract name of the exports to import.
trans-unit.target: Henter Kontraktnavn for Eksporter til å importere.

trans-unit.source: The contract name of the exports to import.
trans-unit.target: Kontraktnavn for Eksporter til å importere.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets the contract type of the export to import.
trans-unit.target: Henter Kontrakttypen eksporten å importere.

trans-unit.source: The type of the export that this import is expecting.
trans-unit.target: Hva slags eksportere denne importen forventer.

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, which means that the type will be obtained by looking at the type on the member that this import is attached to.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>, noe som betyr at typen oppnås ved å se på typen på medlemmet som er tilknyttet denne importen.

trans-unit.source: If the type is <xref:System.Object>, the import will match any exported type.
trans-unit.target: Hvis typen <xref:System.Object>, importen vil samsvare med en hvilken som helst eksporterte.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates that the importer requires a specific <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy"></xref> for the exports used to satisfy this import.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir at import krever en bestemt <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy"> </xref> for Eksporter brukes til å oppfylle denne importen.

trans-unit.source: One of the following values: <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy"></xref>, if the importer does not require a specific <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Én av følgende verdier: <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy"> </xref>, hvis import ikke krever en bestemt <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This is the default.
trans-unit.target: Dette er standard.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy"></xref> to require that all used exports be shared by all parts in the container.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy"></xref>krever at alle brukte Eksporter deles av alle delene i beholderen.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy"></xref> to require that all used exports be non-shared in a container.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.CreationPolicy"></xref>krever at alle brukte Eksporter være ikke-delte i en beholder.

trans-unit.source: In this case, each part receives their own instance.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet får hver del sine egne forekomst.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies the scopes from which this import may be satisfied.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir omfang som denne importen kan oppfylles.
